window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>THE EPIC CONCLUSION!WHERE THE MAP ENDS, THEIR JOURNEY BEGINS... </p> <p>The thrilling saga continues in The Lost Cities, the third and final installment of the electrifying ENIGMA Files series. Rhett, Dinah, and Fabien are back on the path less traveled, their destiny intertwined with the threads of ancient civilizations and inscrutable artifacts.</p> <p>As new worlds open up, reality is blurred as different timelines of events are uncovered. Are the Hand of the Sun really the enemy? Can ENIGMA really be trusted?</p> <p>Can Rhett and company set things right before the many worlds are destroyed forever?</p>"; 
